title: Biden DEMANDS Dem Mayor Downplay Border Crisis
itunes:title: Biden DEMANDS Dem Mayor Downplay Border Crisis
description: A councilmember for El Paso, Texas just claimed the Mayor told her that "the White House asked him not to [declare a state of emergency]" as the city is overwhelmed by migrants. Jay, Jordan, and the Sekulow team discuss this breaking revelation. This and more today on Sekulow.
